                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A ravenous crypt has a 10-foot-space inside of it. A creature swallowed by the ravenous crypt isn't @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed] or slowed, and the creature doesn't need to hold its breath. It can attack the ravenous crypt normally. Because it isn't grabbed, it can't @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Escape] the crypt, but it can break free by dealing bludgeoning damage to the crypt equal to the crypt's Rupture value or by Forcing Open the crypt's doors with a successful @Check[athletics|dc:34] check.</p>"
